data.text: @SenatorBanks You need an ID to drive, buy alcohol, board a flight, buy a firearm, or open a bank account, but not to vote... Casting a ballot that helps determine the future of our country should require at LEAST the same amount of scrutiny as it does to buy a six-pack.

@SenatorBanks @PeaceforallXnew Make Elections Honest Again. 
Re-create Honest money.

@SenatorBanks ID is no problem, but you have failed to show the voters, that by showing thier ID thier ballot will NOT be tagged to that ID. The fact YOU refuse to answer this question, your intent is to track how the voters vote. It is a simple question, and you REFUSE to address the issue.

@SenatorBanks Ana Paulina Luna sadly was played by Thune. He did not want her to hold up Democrats funding package so he lied and told her he would advance SAVE act. Then he backpedaled. He has zero intention of passing it. Now he backed her into a corner. All she can attach it to now is the
